Representative images of IBA-1 immunofluorescence staining in nucleus amygdalae. (C) Quantitative analysis of microglial cell in hippocampus based on IBA-1 
immunofluorescence staining. (D) Quantitative analysis of microglial cell in nucleus amygdalae based on IBA-1 immunofluorescence staining. (E-G) The mRNA 
expression of IL-1β, IL-6, TNF-α in hippocampus. Each dot represents a sample. In image analysis, n = 5 each group. In qRT-PCR analysis, n = 6–8 each group. Values 
